      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="manage_announcement" data-step-uuid="468b6364-d994-4597-ac75-3d1cec24c644">
    <h2 id="manage_announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Manage Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/401/835/original/06861a45-55fb-4a06-9cd7-e0c7bc533baf.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/401/835/medium/06861a45-55fb-4a06-9cd7-e0c7bc533baf.png" srcset="" alt="Manage Announcement" height="186" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A0987B80-1D6E-0135-0925-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To copy a global announcement, click the <strong>Duplicate</strong> icon [1]. Edit the announcement details. Then publish the announcement.</p>
<p>To edit a global announcement, click the <strong>Edit </strong>icon [2]. Edit the announcement details. Then save the changes.</p>
<p>To delete a global announcement, click the <strong>Delete </strong>icon [3]. Then confirm that you want to delete the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
